<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="100%">
<tr>
<td>
<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=index&amp;catid=&amp;topic=3"><img src="images/topics/planesofpower.gif" border="0" Alt="Planes of Power" align="left" hspace="5" vspace="5"></a>
Click on &quot;Read More&quot; to see the Hail text for access to each Plane.<BR><BR>Tier 1 Planes	2<br />
Plane of Knowledge	2<br />
Plane of Tranquility	2<br />
Plane of Innovation	3<br />
Plane of Disease	3<br />
Plane of Nightmares	4<br />
Plane of Justice	4<br />
Tier 2 Planes	5<br />
Plane of Valor	5<br />
Plane of Storms	6<br />
Crypt of Decay (Ruins of Lxanvom)	7<br />
Crypt of Terris Thule	7<br />
Factory Floor (Plane of Innovation sub-zone)	7<br />
Tier 3 Planes	8<br />
Bastion of Thunder	8<br />
Halls of Honor	8<br />
Temple of Marr	8<br />
Plane of Tactics (Drunder, Fortress of Zek)	8<br />
Plane of Torment	9<br />
Tower of Solusek Ro	9<br />
Tier 4 Planes	10<br />
Plane of Fire	10<br />
Plane of Water	10<br />
Plate of Air	10<br />
Plane of Earth	10<br />
Tier 5 Plane	10<br />
Plane of Time	10<br />
<br />
Tier 1 Planes<br />
<br />
<br />
Plane of Knowledge<br />
Access: Default<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
Box of Souls<br />
Find Borik Darkanvil, ask about Box of Souls<br />
Collect Block of Prelium (rare from Plane of Innovation mobs), Crystaline Spider Brain (from crystal spiders in Plane of Valor), and An Agony Mephit Heart (from Agony Mephit).<br />
Either give these items to Borik with 3000pp or combine them with hammer and water in forge (trivial at 250 skill).<br />
Receive Box of Souls<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Plane of Tranquility<br />
Access: Level 46+<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
Thelin’s Torment<br />
Speak with Adroha Jezith, following dialog (get flag)<br />
Speak with Thelin Poxbourne in Plane of Nightmare with 3 groups.<br />
Defeat the Maze, killing Construct of Nightmares at the end.<br />
Receive flag to enter Crypt of Terris Thule<br />
<br />
Alder's Request<br />
Speak with Alder Fuirstel, following dialog (get flag)<br />
Journey into Plane of Disease, battle through the castle, and defeat Grummus<br />
Return to Alder, who asks you to speak with Elder Fuirstel.<br />
Speak with Elder, receive flag to enter Crypt of Decay<br />
<br />
Saving Tylis<br />
After killing Grummus, Elder Fuirstil tells you to kill Bertoxxulous.<br />
After killing Bertox, return to receive flag to enter Saryn’s tower.<br />
Enter the tower and kill Keeper of  Sorrows<br />
<br />
Curing Phanti (unfinished)<br />
Collect Putrified Bubonian Bile from Rythak<br />
Give to ##### she returns purified bile and tells you to talk to an Indigo Orc in Plane of Justice<br />
Give bile to orc (requires Master of orc language), he returns it and requests 3 items.  <br />
Give him Mechanical Clockwork Venom (drop in PoI), Nettling Stinger (Nettling Wraith), and Terror Matriarch Venom Sac (Terror Matriarch).<br />
Return cure for item that allows entry to Plane of Tormet<br />
<br />
Plane of Innovation<br />
Access: Level 46+<br />
<br />
Notable NPCs:<br />
Xanamech Nexmirthafen<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
Wake the Dragon<br />
<br />
Speak with Niatrim Azinok, he requests 3 items.  Return to him a copper node, a bundle of super conductive wires, and an intact power cell.  <br />
When you give these 3 he begins walking towards the untargetable dragon.  After killing your way to the dragon, the gnome wakes it up.  <br />
Kill Xanamech Nexmirthafen.<br />
Hail Niatrim to receive flag to enter Fortress Floor.<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Plane of Disease<br />
Access: Level 46+<br />
<br />
Notable Mobs:<br />
Grummus<br />
Rythak<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
Grimror’s Collection<br />
<br />
Collect 4 items from 4 named mobs in zone<br />
The four mobs are sengian, harrion, scaevian, and generian larva.<br />
<br />
PH for Harrion larva = a malarian larva(not larvae like all the others, spawns near zone in a bit out near flies)<br />
PH for Generian larva = a planarian larva(again just larva, spawns east of castle east of river near pussling camps)<br />
PH for Scaevian larva = a Tsetsian Pupa(just pupa, not pupal, spawns a bit east of generian)<br />
PH for Sengian larva = tachnian caterpillars (in the north part of the zone, not single one close to zone)<br />
<br />
Give the 4 parts to Grimror for a Bangle of Disease Warding which acts as a key to Crypt of Decay.<br />
<br />
<br />
Plane of Nightmares<br />
Access: Level 46+<br />
<br />
Notable Mobs:<br />
An Agony Mephit <br />
A Nettling Wraith<br />
Terror Matriarch <br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Plane of Justice<br />
Access: Level 46+<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
<br />
Trial Quest <br />
<br />
Speak with Mavuin at the back of the Jail area<br />
Say “What information” (receive flag)<br />
Complete 1 of the 6 trials<br />
Speak with The Tribunal and say Mauvin (receive flag)<br />
Return to Mavuin and hail him<br />
Receive flag for Plane of Valor and Plane of Storms<br />
Tier 2 Planes<br />
<br />
Plane of Valor<br />
Access: Complete Trial Quest in Plane of Justice (1 group)<br />
<br />
Notable Mobs:<br />
Aerin’dar<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
Aerin’dar’s Lair<br />
Collect Razorfiend Heart, Crystaline Spider Heart, and Planarian Larvae Heart.<br />
Hail Johon Popoah twice<br />
Go find Paralin Notion and follow dialog.<br />
Go find Master Sergeant Aaramis Daryln and follow dialog.<br />
Go back to Paralin Notion, give 3 hearts to him. <br />
<br />
Collect crystalline orb piece from Luminii Crawler, one of the frogs near the bridgehouse, and one from the skellies. <br />
Return to Master Sergeant Aaramis Daryln, follow dialog<br />
Find Captain Ryglot Cupperhide, follow dialog.<br />
Give 3 orb pieces to Captain Ryglot Cupperhide, receive Orb (key to enter Aerin’dar’s lair)<br />
<br />
Grenic Drere’s quest<br />
Locate Grenic Drere and follow dialog.<br />
Complete the Box of Souls quest.<br />
In Plane of Justice, defeat 3 Tormented Wraiths (near trials room).  Each has a chance to spawn “an exiled soldier/trooper/officer of marr”.  Hand the exiled the Box of Souls, receive box and soul stone.<br />
Give 3 soul stones to Grenic to receive Ring of Marr, which is a key to access Halls of Honor.<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Plane of Storms<br />
Access: Complete Trial Quest in Plane of Justice (1 group)<br />
<br />
Quests:<br />
Wembly’s Revenge<br />
Locate Wembly the Forlorn. Follow dialog<br />
Collect 4 medalion pieces,  uncommon drop from uncomon spawn Diaku Raiders.<br />
Give 4 pieces to Wembly, receive flag for Plane of Tactics.<br />
<br />
Aiding Askr<br />
Collect A storm giant’s head, a beard from the ocean giants, a bone from the desert giants, and a sash from the forest  giants.<br />
Locate Askr, give him the giant’s head, receive containers.<br />
Combine beard, bone, and sash in container and hand to Askr.<br />
<br />
Ask What Bastion of Thunder, receive container<br />
Collect 2 of 3 medallions from named giants, combine them.<br />
Give to Askr, receive flag to enter Bastion of Thunder.<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Crypt of Decay (Ruins of Lxanvom)<br />
